    "aiDescriptions": {
      "short": "Amsterdam, Netherlands-based DJ Martin Garrix delivers Progressive House sounds to global audiences.",
      "medium": "Martin Garrix stands as a prominent figure in the Progressive House scene, known for blending Progressive House, EDM. Their approach to electronic music combines technical precision with creative expression, earning recognition across the international community.",
